{"tid":1147831,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"一個全新、未寫入資料嘅硬碟，同裝滿檔案時嘅重量究竟有無唔同？","createTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T13:23:38.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff12d08d4bf6fc8900a20f9cefd243a8ced0fa8c","tid":1147831,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://Now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNow.com&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=2f7d7cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Now.com</a>】一個全新、未寫入資料嘅硬碟，同裝滿檔案時嘅重量究竟有無唔同？<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/life/player?newsId=347009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flife%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347009&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=af3ac39f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flife%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347009&h=b670ca65\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/life/player?newsId=347009</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-05-06-17-06-54xHk3fz9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-05-06-17-06-54xHk3fz9G.jpg&h=14298349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題似係IQ題整蠱人，相信唔少正常人都會答「新買個4TB硬碟，如果重1kg，寫滿4TB檔案後都係一樣重量，點會唔同咗！就算重咗都因為硬碟殼上面有塵。」<br />\n<br />\n但原因呢條問題完全無玩嘢，係一條正經科學問題，絕無整蠱之意。訊息係有重量嘅，科普YouTube頻道Vsauce就曾詳細解釋Internet嘅重量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WaUzu-iksi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWaUzu-iksi8&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=3fbe53dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WaUzu-iksi8</a>"},{"pid":"f6feef0d2c4d9861499390e65e04bded50d768b6","tid":1147831,"uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"片中舉咗一啲凡夫俗子都可以理解嘅例子 (希望大家真係會明)，一封50K位元組(Byte)嘅普通電子郵件究竟幾重？首先我哋要知道1K有1024 byte，1位元組有8 Bit，所以封電件包含了409600 Bit。<br />\n50 X 1,024 X 8 = 409,600<br />\n<br />\n其中，平均大約有一半嘅Bit係「1」(有電)，另一半係「0」(無電)，所以有204800個「1」嘅訊息需要電容器來儲存，即係總共需要大約80億個電子。一個電子重2 &times; 10&minus;30磅，所以一封50K電郵嘅重量大約係1.6 &times; 10&minus;20磅，相當於21000個鉛原子嘅重量。<br />\n<br />\n即使現今儀器再先進，仍無法計算呢個極端輕嘅重量，所以無法「感受」其分別。<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多，有人真係計咗全球互聯網嘅重量，答案由英國一個科學家搵到，佢據單個電子嘅重量和互聯網所有電子嘅數量，計算出全球互聯網嘅重量等於1個士多啤梨。"},{"pid":"9f036703cfb76c87ef6def3018e1d7561a0431c5","tid":1147831,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"Fun"},{"pid":"cff6687cd98e9d700c19f4c14bc4256170c9fc09","tid":1147831,"uid":183781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6feef0d2c4d9861499390e65e04bded50d768b6","tid":1147831,"uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"片中舉咗一啲凡夫俗子都可以理解嘅例子 (希望大家真係會明)，一封50K位元組(Byte)嘅普通電子郵件究竟幾重？首先我哋要知道1K有1024 byte，1位元組有8 Bit，所以封電件包含了409600 Bit。<br />\n50 X 1,024 X 8 = 409,600<br />\n<br />\n其中，平均大約有一半嘅Bit係「1」(有電)，另一半係「0」(無電)，所以有204800個「1」嘅訊息需要電容器來儲存，即係總共需要大約80億個電子。一個電子重2 &times; 10&minus;30磅，所以一封50K電郵嘅重量大約係1.6 &times; 10&minus;20磅，相當於21000個鉛原子嘅重量。<br />\n<br />\n即使現今儀器再先進，仍無法計算呢個極端輕嘅重量，所以無法「感受」其分別。<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多，有人真係計咗全球互聯網嘅重量，答案由英國一個科學家搵到，佢據單個電子嘅重量和互聯網所有電子嘅數量，計算出全球互聯網嘅重量等於1個士多啤梨。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"士多啤梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673485acae91e0ff56e96ce21dda5604ac5625c9","tid":1147831,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大開眼界"}]}